title: Expat Tales: 27 years on the Gold Coast
text:
Expat Tales: 27 years on the Gold Coast Expat Tales: 27 years on the Gold Coast Next Story Prev Story 12 hrs ago Read more: Stuff.co.nz 
What inspired your move, and how long have you been there? I initially came over for a holiday to see my two brothers who were living here at the time . I found the weather and lifestyle fantastic coming from an Auckland winter.   Stuff.co.nz.
